description:
What is this Abomination of Desolation? When will it happen? And what does mean for us today? 

In Matthew 24, Jesus gives His disciples a list of things that will take place before His return. This chapter has been carefully read and studied by Christians for thousands of years. However, there is one item that has confounded many scholars and has been shrouded in mystery. In this video we will use the Bible to crack the code of the Abomination of Desolation to reveal its hidden meaning. Stay tuned! 

The glory of Heaven is beyond our wildest imagination! However, the BIble does reveal some thrilling truths about this majestic place. Learn how you can secure your place there!
